Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 您怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭 你怎麼了 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說才剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮和阿斯達修的重力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及對大氣的觀測來看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隕石墜落 地震
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異常氣候將會頻繁發生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 三週後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楊以軍事力量鎮壓了蔚藍王國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並施行了戒嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:05:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 國民一定會來救我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整天只和石頭說話而不聽取民意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是報應
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不去理睬被囚禁的國王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們在一個晚上就接受了楊和軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起靠不住的王室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們更歡迎能保護國家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楊一開始的目的就是鎮壓蔚藍王國嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 他的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過不用擔心 可可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跨越了無數的障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次也一定能闖過的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真正的傳說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有被強化過的跡象呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼能激活阿魯迪紐姆礦石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來得仔細研究才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正楊．哈里斯總經理也說過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灌籃假面對他已經沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就任由我擺佈了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但對丹開槍 竟然還搞政變
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了 皮歐蕾特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射殺丹是指揮混亂的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開槍的士兵已經受到懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這不是政變
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楊已經考慮到之後的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒能創造奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不準確
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說從現在開始創造
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了丹和你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯迪紐姆礦石被激活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說子彈才能得以精製
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說子彈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單來說就是強力的炸藥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾天內就能收集到需要的數量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把傳說子彈裝到MOON CANNON裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並用反周波來激活埋藏在月亮上的阿魯迪紐姆礦石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將月球毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣阿斯達修就得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能…那麼月球要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人 朋友 大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楊是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西朵隆 你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在月亮上也有家人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去月球和阿斯達修都會毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲越少越好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露玖 阿斯達修出生的你應該能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月球上的人是多麼懶惰 傲慢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有存在價值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會說服皮歐蕾特的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了創造傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 西朵隆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使拯救了阿斯達修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混亂估計也會持續一段時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候給人們帶來安逸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你們日食的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 日食已經解散了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納比
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為大家都到月球去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果日食解散
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後公主來了 竟是阿蘭的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不清是怎麼回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然多虧這樣才能和大家會合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣的狀況…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們才要盡自己所能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在想來 感覺那個演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了引誘丹的Basquash而提前設計好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿蘭說的通往月亮之路的遺跡也有關嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我先回一趟零號區
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那裡拿些子彈號修理所需的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再去遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹一定沒事的 不是都說笨蛋不會死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納比也一定沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我和阿蘭在這裡等丹然後再去遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要去些地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺跡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納比
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你怎麼說的出犧牲月球這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了嗎 這是為了創造傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 皮歐蕾特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要幹什麼 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是在演戲 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 這是為了誘使楊說出真心而迫不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在在哪裡偷聽也不一定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒能創造出 但是丹的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 他的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救丹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 為了傳說和未來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 要去救他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.87,0:11:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這些數據還是搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹．JD 最接近傳說的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有太多不確定的因素
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以肯定的是沒有剩下多少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以讓我來創造傳說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 把灌籃假面救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們解散了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 但是就解散你們也不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還是偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹 等著我 一定救你出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:30.60,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『主翻』willyer『校正』willyer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到日食竟然來慰問
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真人就是不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無名的勇士們啊 成為傳說的基石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:12:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去救丹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PERFECT Pecchi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 我是丹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死了 要死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼 疼 疼 要死了 要死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在這
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 在軍用設施？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芍詹德博士要解剖他？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解剖…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被超好聞的味道吸引到地下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果在製造咖哩的工廠被抓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後發生了那樣 還有這樣的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你吃掉丹的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我離丹遠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋丸子 振作點 本大爺來看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.95,0:14:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差一點的說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但從調查來看 丹的肉體並無特別
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說的力量要是不駕駛BF的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.67,0:14:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都這個歲數了 在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為 為了下次聚會的餘興節目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要裝嫩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第17度的隕石墜落 直行的有5個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預計墜落區域 蔚藍王國中心地區
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往這條水道去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會有如此巨大的障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.07,0:15:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是傳說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:15:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計算結果出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離月球和阿斯達修相撞還剩下3天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為重力的影響 穆尼斯的電力系統受損
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電力供給下降到20%
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間等丹了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要創造奇蹟的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計畫進入第5階段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快準備 馬上進行發表
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然只能靠我們自己創造了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹…不是傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒呼吸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作 振作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇拉修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是OCB委員會理事長 蘇拉修．肯茲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡 我要告訴穆尼斯和阿斯達修的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個重要事實
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是從太古就流傳下來的創世傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信有很多人也都有聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:18:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月球和阿斯達修誕生於眾神的球類遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後兩顆巨大的行星都被給予了同樣的石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏著能量的石頭 阿魯迪紐姆礦石
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創世傳說的搖籃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這塊石頭磁石般排斥的作用下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩顆行星得以保持距離
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但隨著時間的推移 石頭的力量逐漸減弱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.57,0:18:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月球和阿斯達修被相互的重力吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離在逐漸縮短 不久將…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相撞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相 相撞？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.39,0:18:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.19,0:18:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 相撞啊 是相撞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 傳說還有後續
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹 丹他…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點 丹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是死了 我就不能吃活的了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:18:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋丹 快醒過來 振作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行星是由眾神玩球時創造的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能解決這危機的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有神的力量 巨人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偉大的力量 傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱閃電之球的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的…閃電之球…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BF
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說是這樣記載的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救行星於危機中的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.24,0:19:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籃球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Basquash
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Basquash
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 Basquash
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Basquash…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 用Basquash讓阿魯迪紐姆礦石活性化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.02,0:20:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救月球和阿斯達修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是傳說的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們花了很長時間籌備傳說計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前找到了多位候補者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由這些候補者進行的聯賽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡宣布傳說聯賽正式開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看嗎 在聽嗎 操縱閃電之球的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在月亮上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也快來月亮上進行戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔跑吧 跳躍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越過障礙 到這來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做個了結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Basquasher啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能救你的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說克服了障礙 變得更加耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 阿婆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳動了
