Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹 睜開眼睛 丹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.35,0:22:26.92,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}夜空高懸 清風吹拂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.35,0:22:26.92,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}空は高く風は流れて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.01,0:22:30.23,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}月的鼓動化解在黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.01,0:22:30.23,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}月の波動 闇に融けてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.33,0:22:33.87,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}所以現在只需要向前前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.33,0:22:33.87,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}だから 今は前だけを向き
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:37.07,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Believe Your Love 相信這條路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:37.07,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Believe Your Love この道を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.17,0:22:40.68,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}大海深涵 波濤湧動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.17,0:22:40.68,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}海は深く 波は寄せてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:43.90,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}將你的心靈打動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:43.90,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}きみの心ごわめいていく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:47.48,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}所以現在只需抬頭看天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:47.48,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}だから 今は上だけを見て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.58,0:22:50.85,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Believe Your Love 相信這心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.58,0:22:50.85,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Believe Your Love この气持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.77,0:22:58.02,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}將那嘆息的星座指向
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.77,0:22:58.02,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}嘆きの星座の調べを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.11,0:23:01.24,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}銘刻在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.11,0:23:01.24,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}胸に刻み
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.29,0:23:05.81,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}然後出發前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.29,0:23:05.81,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}そして走り出す
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:09.58,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}我們總是抱著煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:09.58,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}僕らはいつも悩みながら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.63,0:23:13.07,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}尋找那瞬間的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.63,0:23:13.07,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}刹那の希望探している
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.13,0:23:16.29,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}那黑白交織的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.13,0:23:16.29,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}白と黑とが交わるとき
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.69,0:23:19.87,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}一定一定 在那無盡的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.69,0:23:19.87,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}きっと きっと 果てなく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:23.36,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}光的盡頭 會有我們的路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:23.36,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}光の先に 見える道を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.40,0:23:26.67,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}我夢見我們倆走在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.40,0:23:26.67,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}二人で歩く夢を見たよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:30.38,EDTCII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}可愛的 那是我幾近忘卻的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:30.38,EDJPII,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}愛しさ それは忘れていた
